el":"Double Cabins","value":"2"},{"label":"Twin Cabins","value":"2"}],"cabins":5,"bathrooms":5,"length":30.3,"beam":7.54,"draft":2,"hullType":"","hullConstruction":"","tonnage":0,"engines":"3 x 1040 HP Caterpillar","amenities":[{"label":"Air Conditioning"},{"label":"Onboard WIFI"},{"label":"Salon Stereo"},{"label":"Salon TV"},{"label":"Sat Tv"},{"label":"Deck Shower"},{"label":"Bimini"},{"label":"Hairdryers"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Children Allowed"},{"label":""}],"toys":[{"label":"Dinghy"},{"label":"Wave runner Yamaha GP1300 R 2 seats"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear"},{"label":"Wake Board"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards"},{"label":"Water Skis Adult"},{"label":"Jobe Proton 3 seats"},{"label":"Floating Jellyfish protection Pool 5x4m"}],"entertainment":["Salon Stereo","2024 Smart TV in salon 75\"","2024 Smart TV in Owner Suite 43\"","2024 Smart TVs in all other suites 22\"","Sky, Netflix, Prime Video, Disney + ","WIFI Starlink SAT","Internet Package (5G active dual SIM)"],"tenders":["Tender 4.20 m. Novamarine with 40HP outboard"]},"crew":[{"name":"Francesco La Fauci","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::66302670-a654-11ef-94af-49d9e7888b31::assets::4255d1d0-a65b-11ef-8b75-d7d234f93f99/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Italian\nDiploma: Captain 500 GT Sailing and Motor Yachts, Safety and Medical certificates, Open Waters PADI Diver\nSpoken Language: Italian, basic English\nBorn in Messina, Sicily in 1975.\nWith over thousands of nautical miles of experience gathered tin his career, his utmost priority is the safety and comfort of his guests.\nFrancesco with his passionate personality will make your stay an extraordinary experience, sharing with you the most sublime places he knows.\nHe likes to share his passion for yachts with all his guests and will be delighted to help you discover everything you have always wanted to know about sailing and sea. Francesco when not onboard is a professional boating license instructor and FIV windsurfer instructor.\nFrancesco’s favorite sports are Paragliding, Windsurfing, racing regattas."},{"name":"Diana Iaccarino","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::18490529117::vessel::66302670-a654-11ef-94af-49d9e7888b31::assets::e495a2f0-663f-11f0-bc9f-f5d3aca37e50/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Italian\nDiploma: Nautical School Diploma, along with Safety and Medical certificates Born in Pozzuoli, Italy, in 2000.\nDiana Iaccarino infuses her current residence in Tarifa, Spain, with a unique blend of Italian charm and Spanish vibrancy. After completing her education as an officer cadet, Diana embarked on a career in the yachting industry.\nFueled by her passion for maritime adventures and a commitment to excellence, Diana is ready to apply her skills and dedication to enhance the success of any charter. With strong skills in onboard operations, safety, and customer service, Diana aims to enhance charter experiences. Fluent in Italian, English, and Spanish, her multicultural background and expertise make her a valuable maritime team member.\nLanguages Spoken: Italian, English, Spanish"},{"name":"Errico Spada","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::18490529117::vessel::66302670-a654-11ef-94af-49d9e7888b31::assets::f138ce10-663f-11f0-bc9f-f5d3aca37e50/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Italian\nChef Errico hails from Venafro, Molise, and brings a cheerful and accommodating personality to the table. With over 10 years of experience, he is skilled in all facets of the Food & Beverages industry, including bars, conferences, and events. Errico has effectively utilized his unique skill set to tackle challenges, notably on the popular Italian TV show «4 RISTORANTI», hosted by Chef Alessandro Borghese. He has also participated in two additional TV competitions: «Profumi e sapori dall’alto Molise alla Puglia» and «Mare e Monti». In his yachting career he has received numerous positive reviews from his guests.\nSpoken language: Italian and basic english"},{"name":"Giusy Lo Giudice","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::18490529117::vessel::66302670-a654-11ef-94af-49d9e7888b31::assets::fa26b960-663f-11f0-bc9f-f5d3aca37e50/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Italian\nNationality: Italian\nDiploma: First AID (medical care), Imo STCW 95\nBorn in Licata, Sicily, 1985\nGiusy is a very friendly person having an active and positive attitude in all moments.\nHer cheerful, extrovert and sparkling personality combined with diligence and highly professional ethics make her a perfect stewardess.\nShe is a very kind, smiling and polite person guests love to meet during their journey.\nGiusy is Italian mother tongue"},{"name":"Francesco Damasco","avatar":"/media/media::image::c::18490529117::vessel::66302670-a654-11ef-94af-49d9e7888b31::assets::11b21930-6640-11f0-bc9f-f5d3aca37e50/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Italian\nBorn in Monopoli (BA) in 2023.\nAfter his Nautical Diploma, Francesco has joned tha yachting industry. \nFrancesco holds the STWC courses, the nautical boat license, the yacht master offshore and the GMDSS GOC.\nHe is an experienced and committed deckhand with a solid background in yacht operations, navigation, and crew management. With more than four years in the maritime industry, Francesco is  proactive and detail-oriented, taking very good care the safety standards, he manages deck operations, and assists the Captain with all navigational and operational responsibilities. \nFrancesco is discreet, always smiling, attentive and efficient while delivering outstanding service to esteemed guests.\nHe speaks Italian and English."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":3800000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3800000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":4900000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":4900000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"April 1st – May 31st, 2025:","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2025-04-01T00:00:00.000Z",